title: Jay Ellis aka "Lawrence" from Insecure Interview
itunes:title: Jay Ellis aka "Lawrence" from Insecure Interview
description:
Weds 02/08- There's nothing better than having a passionate conversation about your favorite TV show and that's what happened when Jay Ellis who plays Lawrence on the hit show "Insecure" stopped by the Breakfast Club. Angela confronts "Lawrence" over his treatment of women on the show, infidelity, the success of the show, and AIDS awareness in the black community. Comedian George Lopez was the latest recipient of Donkey of the Day and Yee gives listeners advice during Ask Yee.
